(firstQuint)Gabapentin Treatment of Cannabis Dependence.

 This is a 12-week, double blind, placebo controlled, dose ranging study to evaluate the efficacy of gabapentin in treating outpatients with cannabis dependence.

 Counseling and research assessments occur weekly throughout the 12-week treatment phase.

